<Link id="l00364" /><CodeLine lineNumber="364"><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight><Highlight kind="comment"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00365" /><CodeLine lineNumber="365"><Highlight kind="comment">/// Symbol resolution interface.</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00366" /><CodeLine lineNumber="366"><Highlight kind="comment">///</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00367" /><CodeLine lineNumber="367"><Highlight kind="comment">/// Allows symbol flags and addresses to be looked up by name.</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00368" /><CodeLine lineNumber="368"><Highlight kind="comment">/// Symbol queries are done in bulk (i.e. you request resolution of a set of</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00369" /><CodeLine lineNumber="369"><Highlight kind="comment">/// symbols, rather than a single one) to reduce IPC overhead in the case of</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00370" /><CodeLine lineNumber="370"><Highlight kind="comment">/// remote JITing, and expose opportunities for parallel compilation.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
